public abstract class Omnum extends Object
Classis Omnum errōrēs inopīnātōs servat intercipere.
Classem haec classēs omnēs intrā programmāte StrūctorVerba extendit absque classibus et Tenor et Nūntius et manifeste hāc propter natūram eārum.
Officiīs classum Tenor ergō prīmō scrībendus scrīptusque est cōdex sequens:
Thread.currentThread().setUncaughtExceptionHandler(Nūntius.NūntiusErrōribus.fac.get());
